Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SERN will take the time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SERN? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makise Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida Itaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three are coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mayuri is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For FB... FB... FB...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe, get away from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll kill you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make her pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,42.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CRT.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it fails...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mayuri was still in elementary school
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when her grandmother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She went to the grave every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even six months after her grandmother's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she was still going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She always had her grandmother's pocket watch in her hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and she was always, always looking up at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like she was waiting for her grandmother to come and get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then one day, there was a ray of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was the kind called Rembrandt Lighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}or an angel's ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It felt like the light was drawing her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like she was going to disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let it take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be my hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use you for human experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The words that came out of my mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}were from some show I'd seen as a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mayuri and I had watched it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:06:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Some mad scientist, screaming like an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Mayushii is your hostage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I guess I can't go, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you napping?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost five.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going shopping, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll order pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't get the tropical special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.48,0:07:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time leap worked?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mayuri? Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii said she was going to Miss Ruka's, \Nto invite her to the party, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The development conference is canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Canceled?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, go home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay? Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His phone starts ringing, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mayushii.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't answer the phone right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like to leave a message...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:05.67,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's nothing to indicate that the world line changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:08.00,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's different than the D-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.63,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really am back at 5:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:15.68,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the bullet train!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:19.68,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the bullet train is white.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:24.23,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After this, Mayuri will return with Suzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should I go to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, who'd believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.19,0:08:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That I've come from the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Three hours left...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oka... No, Kyouma{\fscx80}—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mayuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thirty minutes ago, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going back to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't she get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so nice of you to invite me to the party, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she say she was stopping anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you see her, tell her to call me right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the world line hasn't changed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then if I don't do anything different,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she should do the same things as last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyan-nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris can't answer the phone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assistant...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, we're done today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home{\fscx80}—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You time leaped from the future, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second you answered the phone, you seemed to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the way you're acting,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can guess that something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have time to give you the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get away from the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Tell Daru, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Ochanomizu{\fscx80}—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Mayuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just invited me to your party{\fscx80}—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn right, up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, which way is Ochanomizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take Nae shopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask at the police box!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once you've taken her, don't come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's the first star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's canceled. I told Kurisu and Daru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I asked Suzu-san to come, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Daru-kun was ordering pizza...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii doesn't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always do things I don't understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:12:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but today, I really don't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really want to do the experiment, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just for now, can you listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain the details later, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Mayushii just got scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rush hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one's at the platform...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the following lines have been shut down, due to a bomb threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they don't know when the trains will start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri, get to the subway now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintarou, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you standing there for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.73,0:13:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, as fast as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mayuri was the one who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Okabe Rintarou has been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,2000)}Mayuri, I will save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Canceled?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got word
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Mr. Braun is planning to return tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin, did you do something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was I too forceful?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't matter if I was acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For now, I just need them away from the lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mayushii.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't answer the phone right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is it taking so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's going to end up like last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to find Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukako! It's me! Okabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oka... I'm sorry, Kyouma{\fscx80}—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mayuri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Mayuri there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just heading bac{\fscx80}—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:52.51,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her not to move until I get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.14,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going back to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:56.18,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:57.68,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:15:59.22,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the bullet train!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the bullet train is white.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was about to go fix Fubuki-chan's costume,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then go to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fubuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cosplay friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said a thread on the costume I made came undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a message from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once it's fixed, I'll go right to the lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll make it to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. The party...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The party was cancel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it was postponed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. {DOKI HAVE INVADED CR}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I wanted you to come with me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Fubuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but do it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're going to be away for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can put Fubuki-chan off till tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is very sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have much time to catch the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mayushii isn't ready at all, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Akihabara Station that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking the subway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:12.44,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a really long time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since you pulled me along like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My watch isn't working...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wound it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sobu line shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut down?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb threat was called in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii has a lot of places she wants to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's okay for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when this is over, I want you to tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have that party sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometime...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri-oneechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to surprise her...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...save Mayuri!
